{"tid":716031,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《掃毒2》開鏡 華仔演金融大亨火拼毒販古仔 苗僑偉演警察","createTime":"2018-06-25T02:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T13:22:29.000Z","uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"78ac1e3671e63d8475911dab8c266bdf2e2f09bb","tid":716031,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"邱禮濤導演、劉德華監製兼主演嘅《掃毒2》已經喺噚日開鏡啦！有網友影到佢哋喺香港開工嘅相片，當中除咗華仔，仲見到古天樂，其他演員苗僑偉、應采兒就未見，呢套戲約投資2億，主景喺香港同菲律賓拍。雖然話係續集，但故事係全新嘅，古仔同華仔表面係大亨，但古仔今次其實係大毒販，華仔係有黑社會背景的金融大亨，兩人唔知點解會出現磨擦，苗僑偉呢個差佬，專捉毒販，套戲就係睇3個點鬥法。<br />\n<br />\n寰宇老闆林小明話導演換咗人，上集係陳木勝做導演，續集導演係邱禮濤，演員又冇咗張家輝同劉青雲，所以唔打算延續上集故事，叫咗編劇寫個新故事出嚟，等華仔拍完呢部戲，就會再拍《拆彈專家2》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180624/large/1529830469_0f1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180624%2Flarge%2F1529830469_0f1b.jpg&h=d02ea30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180624/large/1529830468_a1ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180624%2Flarge%2F1529830468_a1ba.jpg&h=2a109f0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3cd5354bcec278a7412fb56fc33e8ce6b593abf","tid":716031,"uid":75050,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邱禮濤導演、劉德華監製兼主演嘅《掃毒2》已經喺噚日開鏡啦！有網友影到佢哋喺香港開工嘅相片，當中除咗華仔，仲見到古天樂，其他演員苗僑偉、應采兒就未見，呢套戲約投資2億，主景喺香港同菲律賓拍。雖然話係續集，但故事係全新嘅，古仔同華仔表面係大亨，但古仔今次其實係大毒販，華仔係有黑社會背景的金融大亨，兩人唔知點解會出現磨擦，苗僑偉呢個差佬，專捉毒販，套戲就係睇3個點鬥法。<br />\n<br />\n寰宇老闆林小明話導演換咗人，上集係陳木勝做導演，續集導演係邱禮濤，<span style=\"color: red;\">演員又冇咗張家輝同劉青雲，所以唔打算延續上集故事</span>，叫咗編劇寫個新故事出嚟，等華仔拍完呢部戲，就會再拍《拆彈專家2》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180624/large/1529830469_0f1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180624%2Flarge%2F1529830469_0f1b.jpg&h=d02ea30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180624/large/1529830468_a1ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180624%2Flarge%2F1529830468_a1ba.jpg&h=2a109f0b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算佢兩個有份拍，故事都延唔到架啦，唔通拍回魂夜咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11616f568be15c89d87cd0cc178f11bbca0017ca","tid":716031,"uid":35112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"三哥又做警察"},{"pid":"67e4668b752ec6e3f422535250d93e431421bcb5","tid":716031,"uid":46013,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"唔知啊唔知啊唔想知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683d6cae857d1ef751c5c4b88a09a358307b28f8","tid":716031,"uid":46013,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"67e4668b752ec6e3f422535250d93e431421bcb5","tid":716031,"uid":46013,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"唔知啊唔知啊唔想知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"btw無左渣渣輝劉青雲 不如叫門徒2 好過啦"},{"pid":"d22370ccc23b2ffb1244a4cc01bbee74ed63c101","tid":716031,"uid":190789,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"無得唱誓要去 入刀山"},{"pid":"f2167711734851700aa2db76a324dc36e059cd30","tid":716031,"uid":41343,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d22370ccc23b2ffb1244a4cc01bbee74ed63c101","tid":716031,"uid":190789,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"無得唱誓要去 入刀山"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140105/large/05ed18p2new